Package HMS.Models

package HMS.Models
This package contains the core data models representing the entities in the application, such as users, appointments, and medications.
  • Related Packages
    Package
    Description
    HMS
    This is the main package of the project.
    HMS.Enums
    This package contains enumerations used throughout the application for representing fixed values.
    HMS.Menus
    This package contains classes responsible for displaying different menus based on user roles and handling user input in a terminal-based menu system.
    HMS.Systems
    This package contains utitlity classes that manages System logic and store temporary data during run time for fast retrieval and usage.
    HMS.Users
    This package contains classes that represent the user types in the HMS.
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    Appointment
    Represents an appointment between a patient and a doctor.
    AppointmentOutcomeRecord
    Represents the outcome of a completed appointment, including details like service type, prescribed medications, and consultation notes.
    Diagnosis
    Represents a diagnosis with detailed medical information.
    MedicalRecord
    Represents a patient's medical record in the Hospital Management System.
    Medication
    Represents a medication prescribed during an appointment.
    Stock
    Represents a stock entry for a specific medicine in the hospital management system.
    StockReplenishRequest
    Represents a stock replenish request in the system.
    User
    Represents a user in the hospital management system.
